### Welcome to Coder vs. Themer!
This is just a placeholder for now, but ultimately we will host events, announcements, videos, and even schwag related to your two favorite martial code artists.

### Announcements

### Schwag
At some point we'll even have a web store here to sell Coder vs. Themer Schwag!
